beer.beer_description: G’day Straya! This tinny is for me mates cross the ditch. Some blokes and sheilas are still in ISO, using sanny to avoid the rona right now. They just wanna watch tge footy, as straya without Rugbah Leeg ain’t Straya. Aussies wanna have mates over for a barbie with an esky gull of frothies and listen to some Aca-daca after a day pf hard yakka. Dead set, fair dinkum, true blue aussies just wanna have a ripper of a time being able to go down to the bott-lo to get some coldies ( and maybe a goon ) but some are out their being bloody galahs that can’t be stuffed following tge rules. This beer is choca-bloc of Strayan hops. Galaxy and Vic Secreat. Think heaps ( ok lots of slang is both Aussie & Kiwi ) of pineapple and other tropical fruit flavou
